      ],
      "message": "test: cover custom Schnorr nonce callback in ctime tests\n\nExercise schnorrsig_sign_custom with non-NULL auxiliary data and\nwith a distinct custom nonce callback under CHECKMEM.\n\nThe callback delegates to the BIP340 nonce function so the custom\ndispatch path is tested without introducing an unsafe test nonce.\nUse a variable-length message for the custom callback case.",
      "committer": {
        "name": "Yudistira Putra",
        "email": "85178972+Yudis-bit@users.noreply.github.com",
        "date": "2026-07-22T13:58:01Z"
      },
